com.interpss.core.algo.dclf

Interface DclfAlgorithm

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IDclfAlgoLookup, IDclfResult, NameTag, NetworkRef<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithm, EDclfAlgorithm, NetGenAdjustAlgorithm, SenAnalysisAlgorithm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithmImpl, DclfAlgorithmImpl, EDclfAlgorithmImpl, NetGenAdjustAlgorithmImpl, SenAnalysisAlgorithmImpl

    public interface DclfAlgorithm
extends NetworkRef<BaseAclfNetwork<?,?>>, IDclfAlgoLookup, IDclfResult
    A representation of the model object 'Dc Loadflow'. Dclf algorithm object and Dclf calculation method definition. It contains a list of DclfAlgoBus and a list of DclfAlgoBranch.

    The following features are supported:

    • Dclf Calculated
    • Apply Adjustment
    • Adj Max Iterations
    • Adj Tolerance
    • Acc Factor
    • Dclf Solver
    • Dclf Algo Bus List
    • Dclf Algo Branch List
    See Also:
    DclfAlgorithmPackage.getDclfAlgorithm()
